
## Anumantharayan Kottai

Anumantharayan Kottai is a village in Dindigul District in the Indian state of Tamil Nadu. It is on the Dindigul–Kodaikanal Highway, 8 kilometres (5.0 mi) from Dindigul. The nearest railway station is Dindigul, and the nearest airport is Madurai.

# Church 

The world's first church built for St. Ignatius is in Anumantharayan Kottai (அனுமந்தராயன்கோட்டை). It was blessed on 31 July 1822.

